{"tid":2080021,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"完美 超圓潤 球體狀！C Cup激凸身材","createTime":"2020-06-26T07:07:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-26T18:09:47.000Z","uid":109923,"like":1,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"a6b184e37c516406a3e06542088fcded67ca7cd6","tid":2080021,"uid":109923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T07:07:15.000Z","msg":"落選港男梁裕恆（Flow Leung）以大隻見稱，現職健身教練嘅佢擁有47吋胸肌及6塊腹肌，弗爆身材令人羨慕。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Uk6NRLc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUk6NRLc.jpg&h=bb25d4e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢喺社交網上載做Gym時朋友為佢影嘅相，角度由低炒上去影，令其闊實胸肌離奇「變形」，驚變球體狀，網友即笑指目測有C Cup，並建議佢應戴上胸圍，就連佢自己都忍唔住表示：「咩角度嚟，影到個胸肌咁。」雖然身材相當有料，但佢似乎尚未滿意，自言：「未夠乾身，繼續努力！ 」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tGePkDA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtGePkDA.jpg&h=e182b6b6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BL4jHRV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBL4jHRV.jpg&h=358ab8f6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"42f860678a0f1408263bd310f543614d3922cd38","tid":2080021,"uid":252142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T07:07:58.000Z","msg":"想含"},{"pid":"e60c33b4cc9e84ce4173d3899347f3ee155413c4","tid":2080021,"uid":143747,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T07:08:59.000Z","msg":"好撚gay味"},{"pid":"a45ab989bb9e885cbb8df25b784774def5f4f964","tid":2080021,"uid":127425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T07:12:15.000Z","msg":"咪又係鴨一隻"},{"pid":"afa38719f7af485248fbe4c4e7985eef516e8619","tid":2080021,"uid":122134,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T07:14:22.000Z","msg":"第一張睇到扯左係咪正常?"},{"pid":"774891c8d8c6752f7f3479de7089baf80a496d29","tid":2080021,"uid":78492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T07:18:36.000Z","msg":"Bam得"},{"pid":"df1d6bc789f3b0962d73407935afb4a533b93947","t